Birthday greeting website — reusable (no hardcoded name)

SECTIONS
- Hero: fullscreen animated "Happy Happy Birthday To You!" + canvas confetti
- Intro Video: featured player for bdayintro.mp4 with cinematic play button
- Celebrity Greeting Squad: 6 cards grid
- Footer: celebratory message

CELEBRITY SQUAD
- Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson  (dwaynebday.mp4)
- Donald Trump               (trumpbday.mp4)
- The Minions                (minionbday.mp4)
- Africa                     (africabday.mp4)
- Jack Black & Jason Momoa   (jbjmbday.mp4)
- Johnny Sins                (sinsbday.mp4)

INTERACTIONS
- Canvas confetti particles (gold, pink, purple, white)
- Auto-generated video thumbnails via canvas API
- Video modal theater (card click → plays video in overlay)
- Staggered scroll reveal via IntersectionObserver
- Intro video play/pause with overlay state
- Keyboard: Esc closes modal, Enter/Space activates cards
- Responsive grid: 3-col → 2-col (≤900px) → 1-col (≤540px)
